name: Interstellar Ocean Systems
tagline: Taking software development to the next level
body:
## Interstellar Ocean Systems
Organization aiming taking software development to the next level.
That would include creating new ways of engineering of software and possibly requirements for new hardware would be defined on the way.

### Current efforts
Current development focuses on providing open-source development tools and libraries that are useful for developers in their work.

#### Terraforming project
Model transforming toolset
[[http://terraforming.interstellarocean.org/]]
